There is no other way you can be linked with God. If you want to keep yourself in delusion you go ahead with it. But this is the real thing I'm telling you, it's the true thing I'm telling you, for which you should know, you cannot pay, you cannot purchase it, you cannot demand it and you cannot work it out. The grace of God has to come, fall upon you to do it, or a person who is enlightened can only enlighten you.

